Blast in Nigeria’s Northern City of Maiduguri Injures 7 Police, Army Says

-- B y   A r d o   H a z z a d
-- 
2011-07-15T14:55:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/blast-in-nigeria-s-northern-city-of-maiduguri-injures-7-police-army-says.html
A bomb explosion in  Nigeria ’s
northeastern city of Maiduguri today injured seven police and
destroyed their van, Victor Ebhaleme, spokesman for the military
 task force  in charge of security in the region, said by phone.  “No death was recorded,” he said, adding that a militant
Islamic sect, Boko Haram, which draws inspiration from
 Afghanistan ’s Taliban movement, is suspected of being
responsible.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ardo Hazzad in Bauchi at 
 ahazzad@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
